room_title: Escape room "Steampunk" by Alternate Reality Escape Rooms in Houston
room_description:
You and your friends have heard all kind of rumors about this old house and a bitter professor by the name of Hetzel. He is said to be created several brilliant inventions that have never seen the light of day. You and your friends get curious one evening and decide to explore his old Victorian mansion.
As soon as you walk in you realize it was a bad idea... Youâ€™ve just become a part of his game! You and your fellow colleagues have 60 minutes to outsmart him!
